 been throwing around in my head and thinking how I would chage RF to help the server and try to help people maintain sanity so this is what I camp up with.<br>
<br>
Clerics instead of camping the mob for 24/7 until their turn is up would be required to do a manditory (sp?) 12 hour sit.  This can be any 12 STRAIT hours in a single day, every day.  The cleric whos turn it is for RF would be required to do the 24/7 camp and would serve as the time keeper and basically the boss of the camp.  If a cleric is caught cheating, and by cheating I mean logging after 10 hours the cleric who cheated would be forced to stay logged on the entire 24/7 period UNTIL the cleric currently camping RF got his piece.<br>
<br>
I think most people would enjoy this idea because if you can log on early serve your 12 hours and you would be allowed to raid or get an xp grp.  This also would help some electricity costs in your RL house.<br>
<br>
I hope that this idea is warmly received and many guilds and clerics can agree to do this instead of the hell it currently is.<br>
Verant i would like to give you giant @#%$ YOU to you guys for this camp and hopefully you read this board much like you read the FOH board with the changing mana caps GG assholes.  Anyways the final idea to my plan is that the group who just killed RF along with as many people we can all throw together go zone out at strategic time then when the signal is called CRASH THE MOTHER @#%$.  This too would speed up the RF time and call for more happy clerics.  For all of you who say no cause you would get banned - what would VI do ban the whole server.  So help give VI a big @#%$ YOU!<br>
<br>
Anyways tell me what you think<br>
